12-17T00:15:54.000Z","msg":"叫人去佢果度讀完大學仲要選老母科<br />\n畢業先可以出黎姦田<br />\n搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個會去讀老母科，要求咁高點請到人"},{"pid":"15d1b33263e1e604d41ac5faff0726222ed594d6","tid":39012,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:27:06.000Z","msg":"你地香港人就嫌三嫌四啫<br />\n我肯定個政策推行一完大撚把支那人爭住去<br />\n起碼走撚咗先，唔洗吸毒氣<br />\n唔洗賺冥幣<br />\n有冇永住權遲啲慢慢同你爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00344368493fb340b1d47b689b45b8aa1a16e84b","tid":39012,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T18:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b01576fb667a43566cc1a2633199e98fe677818","tid":39012,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T18:42:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}